		"description": "{html}<div><p>Steps to Reproduce:<br>\n1. Install application from bug 3269<br>\n2. Run on device and scroll to and image<br>\n3. Change the orientation of the image</p>\n<p>Actual Result:<br>\nDraws the previous image before displaying the correct content</p>\n<p>Expected Result:<br>\nTo have a smoother transition of the orientation</p></div>{html}",
