					"body": "{html}<div><p>There are other issues resulting from scrollable rotation as\nwell. These include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Jumping to wrong view while in the middle of scroll</li>\n<li>Jumping to wrong view while starting scroll</li>\n<li>Odd behavior during scroll deceleration</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These all seem to stem from the view/content resize and forced\nscroll that happen in the rotation.</p></div>{html}",
